I've filed https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/1272 to track filling out missing parts of our documentation, if anyone has any thoughts on that feel free to ask there or here!

Filling out missing Introductory Documentation 路 Issue #1272 路 bytecodealliance/wasmtime
I'd like to use this issue as a tracking issue for filling out gaps in wasmtime's introductory documentation. This includes our book (rendered), API documentation (rendered), and examples. ...
